# Bundle 30.5 Phase A — visual capture infrastructure for smoke specs.
# tests/visual-captures/<short-sha>[-dirty]/ holds per-run screenshots +
# DOM excerpts + state snapshots + audit windows + index.json. Run
# artifacts — reproducible from spec, gitignored per Q5 answer. Rotation
# policy keeps last 10 SHA dirs locally (oldest auto-pruned at capture
# init). Bundle 31+ may add a baselines/ subdir for diff-regression.
tests/visual-captures/

